{"tid":117784,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"三月的獅子集中討論","createTime":"2017-02-12T13:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T04:04:27.000Z","uid":74536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"561e80b549cb88dee25a71f465b2ad9d82d4a2b1","tid":117784,"uid":74536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/vsh5hfnk9/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fvsh5hfnk9%2Fimage.jpg&h=b91d8afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【STORY】<br />\n獨自居住在東京舊市鎮的17歲少年&middot;桐山零。被周遭歌頌為天才將棋棋士的零，他幼時因意外事故失去了家人。所以生活上、還是棋盤上都背負著深沉的孤獨。在這樣的他面前卻出現了明里、日向、桃三姊妹。與她們的相處後，在零的內心產生出溫暖的心情&hellip;&hellip;各種各樣的人究竟會擦出怎麼樣溫馨的故事呢！？<br />\n<br />\n【STAFF】<br />\n原　　作：羽海野チカ <br />\n監　　督：新房昭之<br />\n角色設計：杉山延寛 <br />\n音　　樂：橋本由香利<br />\n音響監督：亀山俊樹<br />\n動畫製作：SHAFT<br />\n<br />\n【CAST】<br />\n桐山零　　：河西健吾<br />\n川本明里　：茅野愛衣<br />\n川本日向　：花澤香菜<br />\n川本桃　　：久野美咲<br />\n二海堂晴信：岡本信彥<br />\n幸田香子　：井上麻里奈<br />\n高橋勇介　：細谷佳正<br />\n島田開　　：三木眞一郎<br />\n三角龍雪　：杉田智和<br />\n松本一砂　：木村昴<br />\n川本相米二：千葉繁<br />\n幸田柾近　：大川透<br />\n林田高志　：櫻井孝宏<br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://3lion-anime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3lion-anime.com%2F&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ddef690d\" target=\"_blank\">http://3lion-anime.com/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/3_lion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F3_lion&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4935c526\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/3_lion</a><br />\n<br />\n逢星期六 香港時間晚上十點 :  <a href=\"http://mov3.co/nhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Fnhk%2F&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e6bf91f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://mov3.co/nhk/</a> / <a href=\"http://www.zhanqi.tv/meizhi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhanqi.tv%2Fmeizhi&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuC